<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>Welcome to Imaginary Hub X, New Writer!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            color: #2d3748;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        a { text-decoration: none; }
        .email-container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745, #68d391);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 5px 0 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 25px;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #ffd700;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #2d3748;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .features ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .features li {
            font-size: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding-left: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .features li:before {
            content: '✓';
            color: #28a745;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .community-benefits ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .community-benefits li {
            font-size: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .community-benefits strong {
            color: #28a745;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745, #68d391);
            color: #ffffff !important;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #718096;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #28a745;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
        .preheader {
            display: none;
            visibility: hidden;
            font-size: 1px;
            color: #f5f7fa;
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            table { width: 100%; margin: 10px; }
            .header h1 { font-size: 22px; }
            .content { padding: 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="preheader">Welcome to Imaginary Hub X – Start Sharing Your Voice!</div>
    <table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="email-container">
        <tr>
            <td class="header">
                <h1>Welcome to Imaginary Hub X, New Writer!</h1>
                <p>We’re Excited to Have You Join Our Creative Community</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="content">
                <p>Hello <span class="highlight">Amazing Creator</span>,</p>
                <p>We’re delighted to welcome you to the Imaginary Hub X writing community! Thank you for joining us to inspire, educate, and engage readers worldwide.</p>
                <p>As a writer, you’ll have the opportunity to share your unique insights and connect with a passionate group of learners and thinkers. We’re excited to see the impact you’ll make!</p>
                <div class="features">
                    <p><strong>What You Can Expect:</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Publish articles on a platform dedicated to knowledge sharing</li>
                        <li>Receive feedback and support from our community</li>
                        <li>Engage with readers and fellow writers</li>
                        <li>Access resources to enhance your writing skills</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="community-benefits">
                    <p><strong>Community Benefits:</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>In-depth Learning:</strong> Gain access to valuable resources</li>
                        <li><strong>Network & Grow:</strong> Connect with like-minded creators</li>
                        <li><strong>Make an Impact:</strong> Contribute to a global community</li>
                        <li><strong>Stay Updated:</strong> Get the latest trends and news</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center">
                            <a href="https://www.imaginaryhub.in/login" class="button">Get Started</a>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="footer">
                <p>Sent by Imaginary Hub X</p>
                <p>
                    <a href="#">Unsubscribe</a> | 
                    <a href="#">Help Center</a> | 
                    <a href="https://www.imaginaryhub.in/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> | 
                    <a href="https://www.imaginaryhub.in/terms-cond">Terms of Service</a>
                </p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
